OL,6,FA National Grid worker who tortured
OL,7,Fhis friend after falsely accusing him
OL,8,Fof stealing his work tablet has been
OL,9,Fjailed for his murder.
OL,11,FNicholas Ward, 38, inflicted 51 knife
OL,12,Fwounds on 38-year-old Tony McDermott
OL,13,Fin at his flat in Grantham,
OL,14,FLincolnshire.
OL,16,FMr McDermott, a father-of-six and
OL,17,FArsenal supporter, died from heavy
OL,18,Fblood loss after one of the stab
OL,19,Fwounds went all the way through his
OL,20,Fleft leg.
