OL,4,Cfriend over false theft claim jailed
OL,6,FWard, of Eton Street, Grantham, denied
OL,7,Fmurder but was convicted after just
OL,8,Ftwo hours of jury deliberations at
OL,9,FLincoln Crown Court.
OL,11,FHe was jailed for life with a minimum
OL,12,Fterm of 21 years.
OL,14,FWard sobbed during his evidence but
OL,15,Fshowed no reaction as the jury
OL,16,Fdelivered their verdict.JJudge Simon
OL,17,FHirst told Ward: "This was a sustained
OL,18,Fand brutal attack over a period of two
OL,19,Fhours.
