OL,6,F"He tried to escape from both the
OL,7,Ffront and back door of three Eton
OL,8,FStreet but on each occasion you
OL,9,Fdragged him back into the living room
OL,10,Fand continued your attack.
OL,12,F"You effectively tortured your friend
OL,13,Ffor around two hours or so.
OL,15,F"The pain you inflicted on him must
OL,16,Fhave been excruciating."
