OL,6,FProsecutor Simon Ash KC had told
OL,7,Fjurors Ward lost his temper after
OL,8,Fwrongly accusing McDermott of stealing
OL,9,Fhis National Grid work computer on 13
OL,10,FOctober last year.
OL,12,FThe two men - who had been friends for
OL,13,Fover 20 years - were drinking at Mr
OL,14,FWard's home when Ward became violent.
OL,16,FMr McDermott repeatedly denied taking
OL,17,Fthe tablets but Ward did not believe
OL,18,Fhim. The tablets were later recovered
OL,19,Fby police in a bag belonging to Ward.
