OL,6,FThe judge dismissed as "absolute
OL,7,Fnonsense" Ward's claim he could not
OL,8,Fremember the events of that night.
OL,10,FFamily members of Mr McDermott wore
OL,11,FArsenal shirts to address Ward as they
OL,12,Fread victim impact statements.
OL,14,FHis mother described how her son was
OL,15,Fbefriended by Ward 24 years ago.
