OL,6,F"My son was always there for you," she
OL,7,Ftold the court, explaining how Mr
OL,8,FMcDermott had helped Ward through
OL,9,Fbeing bullied, his relationship
OL,10,Fproblems and the loss of his
OL,11,Fgrandmother.
OL,13,F"You tortured him and left him on the
OL,14,Ffloor like a dog," she added.
OL,16,FMr McDermott's eldest daughter
OL,17,Fdescribed her father's death as
OL,18,F"heartbreaking".
OL,20,F"He was trying to get out and you Nick
OL,21,Fwouldn't let him out," she added.
