OL,6,F"You could have stopped but you chose
OL,7,Fto carry on."
OL,9,FThe mother of Mr McDermott's two
OL,10,Fyoungest children told Ward: "You
OL,11,Fstole my baby girls' daddy."
OL,13,FShe added: "You are a monster and I
OL,14,Fpray one day you feel this pain."
